      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Live probes: POST https://exe.dev/exec works for ls/new/rm/ssh-key token generation,\nbut body \"<vm> -- ls\" returns 404. In-VM execution is now:\nmint VM HTTPS token → call https://<vm>.exe.xyz:8787/exec with X-Exedev-Authorization.",
      "originalText": "Live probes: POST https://exe.dev/exec works for ls/new/rm/ssh-key token generation,\nbut body \"<vm> -- ls\" returns 404. In-VM execution is now:\nmint VM HTTPS token → call https://<vm>.exe.xyz:8787/exec with X-Exedev-Authorization.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
